Class Tagpath

java.lang.Object
  com.tailf.jnc.Tagpath

public class Tagpath
extends java.lang.Object

The Tagpath class is used to represent the name of individual schema nodes. Each ConfM SchemaNode is identified by a Tagpath. This class really belongs to the ConfM package, but resides here nevertheless.
